'''BlackBerry PlayBook'''是由开发[[黑莓手機|黑莓手機]]的[[加拿大|加拿大]]通讯公司[[Research_In_Motion|Research In Motion]]（RIM）在2010年9月27日发布的一款[[平板电脑|平板电脑]]。RIM公司希望在10月份将此设备发放给企业用户和开发商，在2011年初开始向消费者发售。<ref name="reuters_official">[http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE68Q59U20100927 BlackBerry maker unveils PlayBook tablet] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE68Q59U20100927 |date=20100928154551 }}, September 27, 2010, [[Reuters|Reuters]]</ref>同时发布的是一款基于[[QNX|QNX Neutrino]]的全新操作系统，[[BlackBerry_Tablet_OS|BlackBerry Tablet OS]]。该系统将运行于BlackBerry PlayBook。<ref name="playbook_pressrelease">[http://www.marketwire.com/press-release/RIM-Unveils-The-BlackBerry-PlayBook-NASDAQ-RIMM-1325727.htm RIM Unveils The BlackBerry PlayBook] {{Wayback|url=http://www.marketwire.com/press-release/RIM-Unveils-The-BlackBerry-PlayBook-NASDAQ-RIMM-1325727.htm |date=20190404044052 }}, official press release, September 27, 2010</ref>

==Android應用程式播放器==
RIM將會在2011年5月推出可於在BlackBerry PlayBook上執行[[Android|Android]] apps的「App Player」軟件。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hk.next.nextmedia.com/template/next/art_main.php?iss_id=1103&sec_id=13724901&art_id=15198478 |title=平板黑馬　 BlackBerry PlayBook |accessdate=2011-04-27 |archive-date=2019-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190924171627/https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==銷情==
RIM在第一季度錄得500,000 PlayBook的銷售額，在第二季度錄得250,000的銷售額，在第三季度錄得150,000的銷售額。因為要降價速銷，RIM需要撇帳4.85億[[美元|美元]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thestar.com/business/companies/rim/article/1095920--dismal-playbook-sales-cause-rim-to-warn-on-earnings |title=Dismal PlayBook sales cause RIM to warn on earnings |accessdate=2011-12-03 |archive-date=2012-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120104222610/http://www.thestar.com/business/companies/rim/article/1095920--dismal-playbook-sales-cause-rim-to-warn-on-earnings |dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/globe-investor/rim-finds-new-ways-to-disappoint-investors/article2257745/ |title=RIM finds new ways to disappoint investors |accessdate=2011-12-03 |archive-date=2011-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111203133534/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/globe-investor/rim-finds-new-ways-to-disappoint-investors/article2257745/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==作業系統更新==
2013年黑莓公司公佈，PlayBook將不會得到BB10作業系統更新。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://techcrunch.com/2013/06/28/blackberry-ceo-confirms-no-bb10-update-for-the-aging-playbook-tablet/ |title=BlackBerry CEO Confirms No BB10 Update For The Aging PlayBook Tablet |accessdate=2013-06-29 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530132016/http://techcrunch.com/2013/06/28/blackberry-ceo-confirms-no-bb10-update-for-the-aging-playbook-tablet/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

